                                        1904
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " to simulate postharvest refrigeration conditions. Then, we acquired hyperspectral images using a SNAPSCAN SWIR camera (IMEC, One Planet), covering the "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        153,
                                        1214,
                                        1205,
                                        1904
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
