                                        1904
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " spectral range. Before imaging each fruit, the acquisition software performed an automatic calibration based on the dark current signal and a high- reflectance standard. For each pear, we acquired four hyperspectral images to consider the whole fruit surface. Following the same procedure, we acquired RGB images of the pear as visual reference both before and after peeling the fruits."
